Author: danju#3943
Content: @ anyone struggling who chose android and is doing pokedex: it may feel EXTREMELY overwhelming to try and understand the ridiculous amount of information you are being thrown at, but you must persevere and keep trying to make sense out of it, little by little. i spent two weeks on and off, sometimes absolutely nothing made sense, but keep watching lessons 1, 2 and 3 again and again - try to make sense out of every line of code written and i believe that anyone will begin to understand. don't feel discouraged, because perseverance will lead to a great reward. if an average joe like me could do it, anyone can. keep on keeping on.
